                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030420-16-off78 t18030420-16-cd79"></join>, a flock-bed, value 20s. a bolster, value 2s. a pillow, value 1s. a pair of sheets, value 4s. a blanket, value 2s. and a great coat, value 40s. the property of 
                     
